<pc>《</pc>
<title>中庸</title>
<pc>》</pc>亦各有解<pc>，</pc>文集<measure quantity="10" unit="chapters">
<num value="10">十</num>卷</measure>
<pc>，</pc>奏議<measure quantity="20" unit="chapters">
